ied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104anu1665702713194.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/anu1665702713194.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/anu1665702713194.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"anu1665702713194\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Use IME for input\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the language-specific input mode in the Input Method Editor.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anu1665702713194__section_w2831ab1b5b1_w2832ab1b5_w2833ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Undefined</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Defaults to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">YIME</code> field syntax code.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">YIME</code> field syntax code, which specifies the\n                           language-specific mode.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"anu1665702713194__table_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">NIME</code>field syntax code, which specifies the\n                           direct input mode.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anu1665702713194__section_phl_yhq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d782888e145\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"anu1665702713194__p_d98963e1_d98964e1_d98965e1\">Switch to the language-specific input mode in the\n            Input Method Editor when focus moves to this string field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"anu1665702713194__section_yjl_zhq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d782888e154\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"anu1665702713194__ul_tkl_13q_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"anu1665702713194__li_d3812e1_d3813e1_d3814e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbr1665702712405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.\">Modeled Field Syntax</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-targe